OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,FThe First Minister has said it is a
OL,8,Fday for "strong condemnation, not
OL,9,Fpolitical nonsense", in the aftermath
OL,10,Fof the suspected dissident republican
OL,11,Fattack on Dunmurry police station.
OL,13,FMichelle O'Neill as well as the deputy
OL,14,FFirst Minister and the Chief Constable
OL,15,Fstood together in united condemnation
OL,16,Fof the car bomb attack, believed to be
OL,17,Fthe work of the New IRA.
OL,19,FA male delivery driver was hijacked in
OL,20,Fthe Twinbrook area of west Belfast on
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,FA device was placed inside the
OL,8,Fvehicle, and he was ordered to drive
OL,9,Fto Dunmurry police station.
OL,11,FThe car exploded outside the station
OL,12,Fas people were being evacuated.
OL,14,FThe incident is being treated by
OL,15,Fpolice as attempted murder.
OL,17,FIt came just weeks after an attempted
OL,18,Fcar bomb attack on Lurgan police
OL,19,Fstation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,FSpeaking at Stormont with deputy First
OL,8,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly and
OL,9,Fchief constable Jon Boutcher, Ms
OL,10,FO'Neill said they were sending a clear
OL,11,Fmessage of condemnation.
OL,13,F"We are absolutely united in
OL,14,Fcondemnation of what has happened,
OL,15,Fnobody wants to see this on our
OL,16,Fstreets, nobody wants to see the fear
OL,17,Fthat that community experienced on
OL,18,FSaturday evening," she said.
OL,20,F"I don't think this is a day for
OL,21,Fpolitical nonsense.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@RO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,F"I think this is a day for strong
OL,8,Fcondemnation.
OL,10,F"This is a day for us to be united in
OL,11,Fsaying these groups have no place in
OL,12,Four society, and it's a day for us all
OL,13,Fto say collectively that anybody with
OL,14,Fany information whatsoever should come
OL,15,Fforward to the PSNI, because these
OL,16,Fpeople need to be dealt with before
OL,17,Fthe courts."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,8,FPengelly added: "I think it's really
OL,9,Fimportant that we do stand very
OL,10,Fstrongly together, that we send very
OL,11,Fclear messages.
OL,13,F"There is a responsibility across all
OL,14,Fof the political parties, particularly
OL,15,Fat a leadership level, to be sending a
OL,16,Fvery clear message, a condemnation of
OL,17,Fthis terrorist attack on Saturday
OL,18,Fnight, but indeed, a very clear
OL,19,Fcondemnation right across the piece.
OL,26,@pD@QOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,F"Terrorism is always wrong. It is
OL,8,Falways without justification, should
OL,9,Fthat have been 10, 20, 40, 50 years
OL,10,Fago or on Saturday night.
OL,12,F"Let's send that clear message, let's
OL,13,Fsend that clear leadership,
OL,14,Fparticularly to our young people
OL,15,Fcoming up, that this is absolutely not
OL,16,Ffor the future.
OL,18,F"It is not our present. It is not
OL,19,Fwanted, and we need to stand together
OL,20,Fagainst that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,FMr Boutcher said an attack on his
OL,8,Fpolice service is an "attack on all of
OL,9,Fus".
OL,11,FHe also appealed for information to
OL,12,Fhelp his officers catch those
OL,13,Fresponsible, adding "before these
OL,14,Fpeople actually harm or kill somebody".
OL,16,F"It's everybody's responsibility to
OL,17,Fcall out these reckless attacks, and
OL,18,Fthat's why we stand here today,
OL,19,Fshoulder to shoulder, in doing that,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@CO]uD@UOUvD@fO]xD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,F"There is no place for these mindless
OL,8,Fthugs, these idiots who think it's
OL,9,Facceptable to carry out such stupid
OL,10,Fattacks.
OL,12,F"I can promise you, we will use all of
OL,13,Four resources to identify them and
OL,14,Fbring them before the courts.
OL,16,F"I want everybody to remember this, an
OL,17,Fattack on the PSNI is an attack on
OL,18,Feveryone, on all of us.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777399866
OL,3,CFirst Minister: 'Not a day for
OL,4,Cpolitical nonsense' after Dunmurry
OL,5,Cstation attack
OL,7,F"Again, I will appeal with anybody
OL,8,Fwith any information about the people
OL,9,Fresponsible to please, please, please
OL,10,Fcontact us before these people
OL,11,Factually harm or kill somebody.
OL,13,F"Please contact us if you know
OL,14,Fsomething, even if you think you might
OL,15,Fknow who's responsible.
OL,17,F"Please, please, please reach out to
OL,18,Fthe PSNI before they actually do kill
OL,19,Fsomebody."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
